  "abstract": "The Board of Governors is amending appendix A of Regulation CC to delete the reference to the Columbia check processing office of the Federal Reserve Bank of Richmond and reassign the Federal Reserve routing symbols currently listed under that office to that Reserve Bank's Charlotte office and delete the reference to the Louisville check processing office of the Federal Reserve Bank of St. Louis and reassign the Federal Reserve routing symbols currently listed under that office to the Cincinnati office of the Federal Reserve Bank of Cleveland. These amendments reflect the restructuring of check processing operations within the Federal Reserve System.",
